## FAQ

### What is the main difference between Claude 4.6 and Claude Mythos?
Claude 4.6 is a general-purpose AI designed for everyday tasks like writing, summarizing, and reasoning. Claude Mythos is highly specialized specifically for cybersecurity, coding checks, and finding digital vulnerabilities.

### Do I need to use Claude Mythos for everyday writing?
No. For general tasks, writing emails, or summarizing articles, Claude 4.6 is actually the better choice because it handles a wider variety of normal topics extremely cleanly. 

### Why do experts call the new Claude Mythos so powerful?
Experts are hyped because it scores a massive 83.1% on difficult security tests, meaning it effectively acts like a highly trained human security professional without making as many careless mistakes.

### Is it hard to understand how these AI models work?
Not at all. You can easily think of Claude 4.6 as an amazing general assistant, while Claude Mythos is a hired security expert. You just pick whichever AI matches the specific job you want to get done!

